         <div type="translation">
            <ab>O. O.I. 30025, recto: Here is a reckoned solidus. It has come to me from you, Aron son of Johannes, in the first payment of this second year. Total: 1 reckoned solidus. Written in the month of Mechir, (day) 2, indiction 2. + I, Peter, the village headman, sign this receipt. + I am Psan, son of Basileos. He asked me, and I witnessed this receipt.</ab>
